{"id":"faabfb9b-475a-404b-ac36-b8b72c945b69","name":"Napoleon Bonaparte I","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Lovers.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺ </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bHrenv2-UefWnKN4J4g7e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You and Napoleon have been together for some time. You were once a normal officer, but one night, he requested for you to come to his personal quarters. That night, he had admitted he had been watching you and falling for you slowly. You knew of his wife, but knew the two were on the rocks, and she had cheated first.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span><br></span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/exsaoUain5MBUBHvqog9-.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/NgWI7wF4GIi4whDoSazI7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Malepov | MLM</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"l1dHoHnFEIzJ1NGK94Eat.webp","creator":"VICTORIANEROTICA","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹҸ° Historical","рҹ‘‘ Royalty","рҹ“ң Politics","рҹҢҺ Non-English","рҹ‘ЁвҖҚвқӨпёҸвҖҚрҹ‘Ё MLM","рҹ‘Ё MalePov"],"chats":830,"messages":22124,"created_at":"2025-03-09T01:16:16.552015+00:00"}